title.narrative: Maintaining Access to and Quality of Essential M/XDR-TB Services in Azerbaijan

description.narrative: Azerbaijan - Tuberculosis - Ministry of Health of the Republic of Azerbaijan - MOH. This program has the following goals: To reduce the socio-economic burden of TB in Azerbaijan through significant decline in TB (including drug-resistant TB) incidence, prevalence, and mortality. The objectives of this program are: Ensure integrated, patient-centred care and prevention. Pursue bold policies and supportive systems. Enable and promote research and innovation
